  • Uses Instruction

  • Add the following line before the </body> of each template or page that you want to use feather icons on.
    
<script src="./../assets/vendors/feather-icons/feather.min.js"></script>
  • Use the icons with the tags <i> or <span>. 
    
<i data-feather="{icon-name}"><i>
<span data-feather="{icon-name}"><span>
  • Initialize feather icon via JS. 
    
<script>
	feather.replace()
</script>
